      },
      "date": "2013-05-17 08:09:48.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nSeparating statahead thread (exit) from statahead RPCs makes code complicated. I'd prefer statahead thread wait for all inflight statahead RPCs finish, and clean them up and then exit. By this way statahead is not guaranteed to quit when ll_file_release() is called, but this should not be an issue. I'll implement this and if all goes well, I'll commit a patch separately.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
